				<ul>
					<li>She almost always wears support tanks and shorts/pj bottoms of some sort. Anything comfy.</li>
					<li>This character is not available for gift sexual artwork of AJ ferret. Please ask permission first. AJ Ferret is married and in a monogamous commitment, so she will not be available for guesting in commission artwork with another character other than Prov Polar Bear.</li>
					<li>Has 2 tattoos. AJ ferret has three solid five-point stars on her left hand between her pointer finger and thumb. The second tattoo is an arm circlet wrapping around the bicep of her right arm, when the ends meet they curl away from each other with an outline of a five-point star on each side.</li>
				</ul>

